<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id7a2c4926-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s7708"><num value="7708">§ 7708.</num><heading> Territorial participation</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary of State shall ensure participation in the Commission and its subsidiary bodies by the Commonwealth of the Northern Mariana Islands, American Samoa, and Guam to the extent allowed under United States law.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id7a2c4927-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/114/327/tI/s108">Pub. L. 114–327, title I, § 108</ref>, <date date="2016-12-16">Dec. 16, 2016</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/130/1984">130 Stat. 1984</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
